ext_descriptions.ext_description:
A main type is a STRING which indicates, whether a Building_element_component is the main component of a . This shape is modified through the additional Building_element_component to give the final shape of the . The predefined value of the main is one of the following:
main;
not_main.

An opening_functional_type specifies a descriptive label that indicates the form or function of the Opening by a predifned value.
The predefined value of the opening_functional_type is one of the following:


door_opening;

service_opening;

window_opening.
